==German==
===Etymology===
{{OHG.}} ''[[fenstar]] n, [[finstra]];''{{L.}} ''[[fenestra]]''. The neutral genus seems to be derived from the older word ''[[ougatora]]'', literally meaning "door in the form of an eye", from words for [[Auge]] and [[Tor]] ''n''.

===Noun===
'''das Fenster''' ('''plural''' Fenster)

# A [[window]].

